data.description: WOW! This is the home of your dreams. This home says take me now! Large fenced yard that is professionally landscaping w/concrete patio. 8x10 shed. Open kitchen/dining concept with white custom cabinetry, l granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, 6" wide cherry wood man-made pre-finished hardwood flooring creating a beautiful contrast design. Laundry chute, porcelain tile baths. Ceiling fans in all 3 bedrooms.  Professionally landscaped with large fenced back yard w/ concrete patio and 8' x 10' storage shed. 2.5 car attached garage. Full basement with rec room and tons of storage space. Unique features available in this home including roof and windows (2007), whole house generator (2021). and beautiful perennials in the yard. Well-maintained home with cedar stained (2021), Tuckpointed (2022), water heater (2021), some floors (2021). Many upgrades were done by previous owners including radon mit system. Beautiful built-ins. More storage than stuff! Too much storage. This yard is perfect for the entertainer, gardener, and/or the person who loves to just enjoy a peace for place to reset. H&B due 04/08/24 @ 9am
